    <title>最近点对问题</title>
    <link href="http://luxinyu1.github.io/2020/04/03/%E6%9C%80%E8%BF%91%E7%82%B9%E5%AF%B9%E9%97%AE%E9%A2%98/"/>
    <id>http://luxinyu1.github.io/2020/04/03/%E6%9C%80%E8%BF%91%E7%82%B9%E5%AF%B9%E9%97%AE%E9%A2%98/</id>
    <published>2020-04-03T15:37:48.547Z</published>
    <updated>2020-04-04T14:33:47.759Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>暴力算可以。但分治法时间复杂度明显更低。</p><h3 id="分治法"><a href="#分治法" class="headerlink" title="分治法"></a>分治法</h3><p>其实和最大子段和是大同小异的。<br>划分：根据x坐标对S中的点按升序排序，在中间点处将整个平面一分为二。</p><ol><li>最近点对在左边，设其为d1</li><li>最近点对在右边，设其为d2</li><li>最近点对横跨了两个区  </li></ol><p>显然对于1，2，只要递归即可，但对于3，寻找一个好的解决方案就很重要了。</p><ol><li>对左右点集双重遍历，分治法等于白做。</li><li>用递归生成的d1和d2，算dmin=min(d1, d2)，显然，<strong>在中心线+-dmin范围外的点不用参与计算了</strong>，但最坏情况（即所有点都集中在+-dmin区域中）下的时间复杂度与1相同。  </li></ol><p>改进一下2，通过观察可以发现，以中轴线为中心的的2dmin*dmin空间内至多含有8个点，故最近点对必在T[i]到T[i+7]中，故只需将T从小到大排序，选下标连续的8个点算距离即可。</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">cp(S[], Y[], low, high) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">    if (high - low &lt;&#x3D; 3) then</span><br><span class="line">        mid &#x3D; (high - low) &#x2F; 2</span><br><span class="line">        x0 &#x3D; S[mid].x</span><br><span class="line">        d1 &#x3D; cp(S, low, mid) &#x2F;&#x2F; 子问题1</span><br><span class="line">        d2 &#x3D; cp(S, mid+1, high) &#x2F;&#x2F; 子问题2</span><br><span class="line">        dmin &#x3D; min(d1, d2)</span><br><span class="line">    for i &#x3D; 1 to n</span><br><span class="line">        if (|x(Y[i]-x0)|&lt;&#x3D;dmin) then</span><br><span class="line">            k &#x3D; k + 1</span><br><span class="line">            T[k] &#x3D; Y[i] &#x2F;&#x2F; 选出T[k]</span><br><span class="line">    dmin2 &#x3D; dmin</span><br><span class="line">    for i &#x3D; 1 to k-1</span><br><span class="line">        for j&#x3D;i+1 to min&#123;i+7, k&#125;</span><br><span class="line">            if d(T[i],T[j]) &lt; dmin2 then dmin2 &#x3D; d(T[i],T[j])</span><br><span class="line">    dmin &#x3D; dmin2</span><br><span class="line">    return dmin</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>]]></content>
    
    <summary type="html">
    
      
      
        &lt;p&gt;暴力算可以。但分治法时间复杂度明显更低。&lt;/p&gt;
