    <title>快速排序</title>
    <link href="http://luxinyu1.github.io/2020/03/26/%E5%BF%AB%E9%80%9F%E6%8E%92%E5%BA%8F/"/>
    <id>http://luxinyu1.github.io/2020/03/26/%E5%BF%AB%E9%80%9F%E6%8E%92%E5%BA%8F/</id>
    <published>2020-03-26T07:41:48.525Z</published>
    <updated>2020-04-02T07:34:33.683Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>快速排序<strong>仍然采用了分治法的思想</strong>，只是在其基础上引入了哨兵，实现了<strong>跨度更大</strong>的交换。因此，主程序实现用递归显得更加简单和清晰。</p><figure class="highlight c"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="function"><span class="keyword">void</span> <span class="title">QuickSort</span><span class="params">(Type a[], <span class="keyword">int</span> p, <span class="keyword">int</span> r)</span> </span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">if</span> (q &lt; r) &#123; <span class="comment">// 仅仅确保它是个合法数组</span></span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">int</span> q = Partition(a, p, r); <span class="comment">// 表面切分数组，获得哨兵q的位置与一个全部比q小的数组切分，一个全部比q大的数组切分</span></span><br><span class="line">        QuickSort(a, p, q<span class="number">-1</span>); <span class="comment">// 子问题求解</span></span><br><span class="line">        QuickSort(a, q+<span class="number">1</span>, r);</span><br><span class="line">    &#125;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>很显然Partition是这个算法的精髓。</p><figure class="highlight c"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="function"><span class="keyword">int</span> <span class="title">Partition</span><span class="params">(Type a[], <span class="keyword">int</span> p, <span class="keyword">int</span> r)</span> </span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">int</span> i = p;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">int</span> j = r + <span class="number">1</span>;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">int</span> x = a[p];</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">while</span>(True) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">while</span> (a[++i] &lt; x); <span class="comment">// 找到比x大或等于x的左边区元素下标，准备换到右边</span></span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">while</span> (a[--j] &gt; x); <span class="comment">// 找到比x小或等于x的右边区元素下标，准备换到左边</span></span><br><span class="line">        <span class="comment">// 上面造成的结果就是标兵与比其大/小元素反复左右大跨度交换，i和j下标对应的元素交替为标兵</span></span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">if</span> (i &gt;= j) <span class="keyword">break</span>; <span class="comment">// 这一句放在实际交换之前，i = j时将陷入死循环，i,j都为标兵的最终位置，必须退出</span></span><br><span class="line">        swap(a[i], a[j]);</span><br><span class="line">    &#125;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">return</span> j; <span class="comment">// 也可以return i</span></span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>不过想一想，每次都初始化同一个哨兵位置是最合理的吗？显然不是，当分治时一边为0个元素，中间为哨兵，另一边为n-1个元素时，陷入了最坏的情况，与插入排序差不多慢，算法导论上有详细的说明。<strong>所以可以增加一点随机性去规避极端性</strong>：</p><figure class="highlight c"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="function"><span class="keyword">int</span> <span class="title">RandomizedPartition</span><span class="params">(Type a[], <span class="keyword">int</span> p, <span class="keyword">int</span> r)</span> </span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">int</span> i = Random(p, r);</span><br><span class="line">    Swap(a[i], a[p]);</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">return</span> Partition(a, p, r)</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>快速排序在常数倍分割时时间复杂度为O(nlogn)，在最坏条件下（一边为0个元素，中间为哨兵，另一边为n-1个元素）时，时间复杂度为O(n^2)</p>]]></content>
    
    <summary type="html">
    
      
      
        &lt;p&gt;快速排序&lt;strong&gt;仍然采用了分治法的思想&lt;/strong&gt;，只是在其基础上引入了哨兵，实现了&lt;strong&gt;跨度更大&lt;/strong&gt;的交换。因此，主程序实现用递归显得更加简单和清晰。&lt;/p&gt;
